data.title: Joyce Genealogy
data.text:
11975. Mary Anne Brewster. Born on 10 Dec 1660 in Norwich, CT.142 Mary Anne died in Guilford, CT, on 2 Dec 1750; she was 89.142

11978. Dea. Daniel Brewster. Born in Mar 1667 in Norwich, CT.142 Daniel died in Preston, CT on 7 May 1735.142

Daniel served as a Justice of the Peace, Representative to the General Court, Lieutenant and Captain of the militia, and as deacon of the First Church in Norwich.142
